To add ansible host entry as below:

sudo vi /etc/ansible/hosts

[testgroup]
kslave1 ansible_host=172.31.3.159
======================================================



To run playbook commands:

ansible-playbook <playbook-name.yaml>


====================================================


Ad-hoc commands:

ansible all -a "free -m"
ansible all -a "df -h"
ansible all -a "uptime"
